      <h3>Why SmartyPants Women's Complete Is Our Top Pick</h3>

      <p>SmartyPants Women's Complete earns the top position because no other women's gummy multivitamin packs this many clinically relevant nutrients into a single product. The formula includes omega-3 DHA and EPA from fish oil (for heart and brain health), methylfolate (the bioactive form of folate that bypasses MTHFR conversion issues), CoQ10 (for mitochondrial energy production), vitamin D3, vitamin K2, a complete B-complex, biotin, and zinc. This is effectively a multivitamin, omega-3, and CoQ10 supplement combined into one.</p>

      <p>The methylfolate inclusion is particularly important for women of reproductive age. Approximately 40% of women carry an MTHFR gene variant that impairs the conversion of synthetic folic acid into its active form. By using methylfolate directly, SmartyPants ensures reliable folate delivery regardless of your genetic profile. The 288mcg of omega-3 (DHA + EPA) also sets this apart — most women's gummy vitamins contain zero omega-3s because fish oil is difficult to formulate in gummy form.</p>

      <p>The trade-off is serving size. At 6 gummies per day, SmartyPants demands more commitment than the 2-gummy-per-day standard. The $0.90 per serving price also positions this at the premium end. However, when you calculate the cost of buying a separate multivitamin, omega-3, and CoQ10, SmartyPants actually delivers superior value. For women who want one product to cover the broadest possible nutritional base, this is the clear winner. If you are planning a pregnancy, also review our guide to the <a href="/best-prenatal-gummies/">best prenatal gummies</a> for pregnancy-specific formulations.</p>

